bio: Inga lives in Plains District of the city of Whiterun. She is a Nord woman with turquoise eyes and long brown-auburn hair, which she usually keeps tucked under her white chef's hat. She lives alone in the back of her small shop, named Tundra Bakery. She is a skilled baker who sells a wide assortment of delicious baked goods, such as breads, pies, tarts, biscuits, etc.
name: Inga
